==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Syncarp
<hw>Syn"carp</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>syncarpium</ets>. See <er>Syncarpous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A kind of aggregate fruit in which the ovaries cohere in a solid
mass, with a slender receptacle, as in the magnolia; also, a similar
multiple fruit, as a mulberry.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Syncarpium</ent>⟦br⟧
